task.summary: Default task
Remove previous config classes (all autowired now).
Tweak log configuration.
Autowire sender/receiver in the controller instead of the app.
Enable autocommit.
Remove obsolete info from README.
Preliminary work on Executors.
Change the receiver to get json-serialized payloads.
Simplify the Executor interface.
New signature for publish method. It accepts now an open list of parameters to convert to a JSON payload.
Tweak documentation and logs.
Pretty printing of json and set placeholders.
Replace placeholders in the trigger with their actual value.
Update doc.
Update doc.
Adapt test cases to the Sender/Receiver with an open list of parameters.
Asynchronous execution of Local Command. Add Working Dir settting to the configuration.
Activate both Local and Remote executors. Move common logic to the base executor.
Migrate to spring boot 2.2.0.
Add packaging tools. Execute as standalone App.
First docker version.
Work on external file configuration.
Advance version to 1.0.
Execute local commands with an SSH wrapper when running inside a docker container.
Install openSSH inside the docker image.
Log the wrapped command.
Check also that the user host is set.
Do not check the host key when submitting the ssh wrapper. Log sterr/out from the command.
Fix ssh wrapper.
New MODE setting for executors. If set to BLOCKING, the executor waits until the process triggered by the message terminates and logs its output.
Send back the reply message only if the process is still alive or exit value is zero.
Reorganize documentation. Add information to start an instance with Docker.
Extend configuration doc.
Complete the configuration section of the documentation.
Add info on remoted calls.
Clean up README.
Clean up unused code.
Update readme with build instructions.
Document Payload, Actions and Interface.
Refactor as multi-module project. A module for the backend executors and another module for the actual kafka service.
Increase version to 1.1 in the run scripts.
First stub of the Azure EventHubs-Dispatcher Service.
Reorganize the documentation. Add readme for the EventHubs service.
Doc: Fix title in the readme.
Remove test files.
Update gitignore.
Tweak readme.
Define a file log appender for the kafka-service.
Add callback to send method to log failures when messages are sent.
Add and configure a Junit test for the EventHubs' DispatcherController.
